SUMMARY:Pediatric Grand Rounds: Reflections on Parenting
LOCATION:Hybrid: Dell Children’s Medical Center Signe Auditorium & Zoom
DESCRIPTION:In this installment of Pediatric Grand Rounds and the fifth ann
 ual George Edwards Lectureship\, Andrea G. Asnes \, M.D.\, M.S.W\, present
 s “Reflections on Parenting: Adequacy\, Threats to Adequacy\, and the Impa
 ct of Practice\, Programs and Policies.” Asnes is a professor in the Depar
 tment of Pediatrics at Yale School of Medicine. She was also the chief in 
 the section of Child Safety\, Advocacy & Healing in the Department of Pedi
 atrics at the Yale New-Haven Hospital. Email Pam Knight for the Zoom link.
 \\n\\nEvent page: https://dellmed.utexas.edu/events/pediatric-grand-rounds
 -reflections-on-parenting
URL:https://dellmed.utexas.edu/events/pediatric-grand-rounds-reflections-on
 -parenting
END:VEVENT
